<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
  <head>
    <title>Template Manager</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>

  <body style="background-color: ">
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function() {
    Materialize.updateTextFields();
  });
        
    </script>
  <header>
  </header>
  <main style="padding-left: 0;">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 5%;">
      <div class="row">
      	<div class="col m2"></div>
        <div class="col s12 m8">
          <div class="card blue-grey darken-1 horizontal">
          	
          	<div class="card-image">
        		<!--<img src="https://lorempixel.com/100/190/nature/6">
        		<i class="material-icons dp48">settings</i>-->
      		</div>
            
            <div class="card-stacked">
            	<div class="card-content white-text">
            		<span class="card-title">Setup Wizard: Administrator Account (3/3)</span>
              <p>Administrator account is going to be the first user in the system. Only administrator can edit global preferences, eg API endpoint details, RDP master credentials and Dev toggles. Make sure you keep your credentials somewhere safe!</p><br>

              <p>Password must be longer than 6 characters!</p><br>

            	  <div class="row">
        <%= form_for User.new, :url => {:action => "masterinitialize"}, remote: true do |f| %>
      <div class="row">
    <div class="input-field col s6">
      <%= f.text_field :email, { class: "validate", required: true, autocomplete: "off" } %>
      <label>E-mail address</label>
    </div>
        <div class="input-field col s6">
      <%= f.text_field :password, { class: "validate", required: true, type: "password", autocomplete: "off" } %>
      <label>Password</label>
    </div>
      </div>
      <%= f.submit "Save settings", {class: "waves-effect waves-light btn", remote: true} %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
            	</div>
        	<div class="card-action">
          		<a href="<%= setup_done_path %>">Next step >> Finalize Setup</a>
        	</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col m2"></div>
      </div>
</div>
  </main>
  </body>
</html>

<br>